                                                                                                                                                                                                     Tennis
                      
	Washington: Somdev Devvarmans impressive run at the $508,000 Legg Mason Tennis Classic tournament was halted when he lost his quarterfinal tie in straight sets against Igor Kunitsyn.         
	Playing his first ATP tour tournament, qualifier Somdev lost 4-6, 1-6 against the world No. 84 Russian in the hard court event last Friday.                                                                                                                          
